      "PDF (Portable Document Format) is the universal standard for sharing documents that need to look identical on any device and operating system. While PDF is most associated with text documents, it is also the ideal format for sharing collections of images professionally — a photo portfolio, a client proof set, a scanned document collection, a real estate listing with multiple photos, or a product catalog. Converting images to PDF preserves quality, maintains the exact layout you specify, and creates a single file that is easy to email, print, and archive.",
